{"id": 2550, "genre": 1000, "title": "上网时你都有哪些“极简主义”的习惯？", "description": "不要推送不要分享不要下载不要猜你喜欢，我只想清清静静地网上冲个浪谢谢。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Anna_Isaeva）", "record_count": 32802, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180929141455NKAqrYxw5h8gjnac.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-08T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4757, "title": "上网时你都有哪些“极简主义”的习惯？", "content": "上网时你都有哪些“极简主义”的习惯？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 301481, "content": "用比较“轻”的网页版/小程序代替下载app", "image": "img/option/option/201809302007158sFrYPpc37vnalTx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301482, "content": "同类型的app，一般都是选最占用内存最少的那个", "image": "img/option/option/20180930202209vYNaeTn9MiBGUcF8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301483, "content": "打开新app，第一步就是关掉分享/推送/资讯/猜你喜欢", "image": "img/option/option/20180930202148bwOl9SBiU6MPYNCn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301484, "content": "官方应用臃肿，改用第三方版本（国际版是个好东西", "image": "img/option/option/20180930202319lgsxROtD9LVaZcNr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301486, "content": "浏览器/搜索引擎，我只用首页没新闻、不会天天提示“设为默认”的那一款", "image": "img/option/option/20180930201758vrLUPJa92k5lCITK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301488, "content": "手机主屏幕尽量保持 1-2 页，不用划来划去", "image": "img/option/option/20180930202043rgmfGP9tQULF3aZ7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301489, "content": "只保留几个常用应用，其他长期不用的就会删掉", "image": "img/option/option/20180930201708L4rJRqf0Fu6pYaw9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301491, "content": "系统自带的 app，如果好用就不会另外下载第三方的", "image": "img/option/option/20180930201223SKbp7kZmOj62PTtw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 301492, "content": "照片定期清理/转移，不会长期积压在手机里", "image": "img/option/option/20180930203441Bj8srTAFmf4DbRdS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}